topIssues.title: Feature Request: Add CometAPI Provider Support
topIssues.author: TensorNull
topIssues.body:
Request to add **CometAPI** as a supported LLM provider

## CometAPI Resources
- Website: https://www.cometapi.com/
- API Documentation: https://api.cometapi.com/doc
- Base URL: https://api.cometapi.com/v1/
- Model List: https://api.cometapi.com/v1/models
- Get API Key: https://api.cometapi.com/console/token
- Pricing: https://api.cometapi.com/pricing

## Implementation Offer
We can implement this integration and submit a PR according to your project's standards and guidelines if you'd like.
